<p>Today we have another quick screencast answering a question in <a href="drupalcommerce.org/questions">the Q&amp;A section of drupalcommerce.org</a>. This user, golubovicm, has asked <a href="http://www.drupalcommerce.org/questions/12597/edit-own-products-permission-not-working">"Edit own products permission" is not working!</a> First off, that's not the best way to phrase a question, but it does happen that <a href="https://drupal.org/node/1919100">a number of people</a> are wondering how to set up a user to create, edit, and delete their own products. So, we've created <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJ8CljQ_2z0&amp;feature=youtu.be">a quick screencast</a> to walk you through how to set this up.</p>
